## Getting Started
### Logging In
1. Navigate to the login page
2. Enter your email and password
3. Click "Login"

### Dashboard Overview
- Quick statistics
- Recent sales
- Low stock alerts
- Daily sales chart

## User Roles
### Administrator
- Full system access
- Manage users
- View reports
- Configure system settings

### Cashier
- Process sales
- View products
- Generate receipts

## Using the POS Interface
### Making a Sale
1. Search for products
2. Add items to cart
3. Apply discounts if needed
4. Process payment
5. Generate receipt

### Payment Methods
- Cash
- Card
- Mobile Payment

